wdi2-SH.MED.SAOP.P5.def: Specialist surgical workforce is the number of specialist surgical, anaesthetic, and obstetric (SAO) providers who are working in each country per 100,000 population.
wdi2-SH.MED.SAOP.P5.name: Specialist surgical workforce
